originalText.text: Jonathan Anapol is the best. I had a long tedious negotiation that kept stalling and stopping and stalling and stopping. It lasted over a year. At one point the deal even fell thru. This never deterred Jonathan. He stuck with it all the way and never complained even when the deal was dead. He was professional and always on time and really fought to get me the best deal. I recommend his very highly, class act all the way!

originalText.text: Jonathan and his team were incredibly attentive and knowledgeable. We were under the gun to find a new space in Manhattan and he definitely came through - and made the process as smooth as possible. We definitely recommend Jonathan (and Prime Manhattan Realty), as he was a pleasure to work with and very trustworthy throughout the process. Feel free to reach out to him and his team for any and all questions - you will find they are very welcoming.

originalText.text: I was looking for a luxurious office space in the Plaza district in NYC for my financial investment firm. I was fortunate enough to get referred to Scott Bennett , who is a broker for Prime Manhattan Realty.He may experience so wonderful I had to write a review I want anyone to know if they’re looking for the best commercial broker in NYC Scott Bennett is the person! He knows and understands the business like no other. He has been in the field for so many years and has so many connections and resources. He not only got me the best deal but he help me understand the nuances of closing and negotiating a deal. He was the most genuine voice in a market place I’ve ever met. He sat down with me and really listen to my needs and wants. It seemed like he was available 24/7. He answered all my questions. He was such a pleasure to be around I felt like  he was my best friend. I highly recommend Scott for anyone’s Commercial Real-estate needs.
